How Do You Think Technology Affects Dating?

Have you had any experience with dating? Have you ever used dating apps? If so, what has it been like for you? If not, why not?

How do you think technology — like apps, Netflix, social media and texting — affects dating and relationships? In your opinion, does it improve or worsen romantic interactions? How so?

---

In my opinion,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: can be effective in helping people find their significant others.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It is important to remember that technology has always affected dating for about the past century, and it has only gotten increasingly available, efficient, and

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: modern comforts that make dating easier for people.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: With these in mind, technology actually improves the way people interact with each other.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Technology can improve communication and relationships, by allowing people to see and hear each other.
